data.oai_dc:dc: Datasets for the MS FE 2017 00585 R1

This Excel file contains all the data used in the study published in Functional Ecology present paper. This file has three Excel spreadsheet : 1) Data used for the linear models (part 1 of the paper) , 2) Data used for the T-statistics (part 2 of the paper) , 3) Data used for the Hypervolume calculus (part 3 of the paper).
